-- ===== AI Presentation (10 tools) =====

-- Tome
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Tome?</h2><p>Tome is an AI-native presentation and storytelling platform that creates complete, narrative-driven decks from a single text prompt. Instead of thinking in individual slides, Tome thinks in stories — structuring your content around a narrative arc with visual cohesion throughout. It is the go-to tool for founders crafting investor pitches, teams building internal memos, and anyone who values storytelling over bullet points.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Complete deck generation from a single text prompt. A narrative-first approach that structures content as a story. Built-in DALL-E image generation fills slides with relevant visuals. Loom video embeds bring presentations to life. Real-time analytics track viewer engagement and time spent on each page.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan covers core features. Pro at $20/month per user unlocks unlimited creation, analytics, and custom domains. Enterprise plans offer advanced security and admin controls.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'tome-app';

-- Gamma
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Gamma?</h2><p>Gamma is an AI creation tool that generates polished presentations, documents, and even websites from a text prompt or outline. Its card-based editor gives you more layout flexibility than traditional slide tools, while the AI handles design and visual consistency automatically. Gamma has rapidly become one of the most popular AI presentation tools thanks to its strong free tier and beautiful default designs.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Three creation modes: presentation, document, and website. AI generates complete decks in seconds from text prompts. A flexible card-based layout breaks free from rigid slide grids. Audience analytics track views and engagement. Rich media embedding supports videos, charts, and interactive content.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes 400 AI credits and Gamma branding. Plus at $15/month per user removes branding and provides unlimited credits. Pro plans add custom fonts and advanced features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'gamma-app';

-- Beautiful.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Beautiful.ai?</h2><p>Beautiful.ai is a presentation tool that automatically designs your slides as you add content. The magic is in the smart templates — as you type, resize images, or add data, the layout adjusts in real time to stay visually balanced. DesignerBot can also generate entire presentations from a single prompt. It is the best option for people who need professional-looking decks but are not designers.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 60 smart slide templates that auto-adapt to your content changes. DesignerBot generates full presentations from text prompts. Brand kit enforcement ensures visual consistency across teams. Viewer analytics show how people engage with your decks. PowerPoint and PDF export for sharing outside the platform.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Pro starts at $12/month (billed annually). Team at $40/user/month adds collaboration and analytics. Enterprise plans offer advanced admin and security controls.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'beautiful-ai';

-- SlidesAI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is SlidesAI?</h2><p>SlidesAI is a Google Slides add-on that uses AI to generate presentations from text. If you already live in the Google Workspace ecosystem and do not want to learn another tool, SlidesAI slots right into your existing workflow. Paste your text, select a theme, and it builds a complete slide deck directly inside Google Slides — ready to share through Google Drive like any other file.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Native Google Slides integration runs entirely within Google Workspace. AI converts text, articles, and prompts into complete slide decks. Multiple theme options control the visual direction. Built-in image search finds relevant visuals automatically. Multilingual support covers presentations in various languages.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes 3 presentations per month. Basic at $10/month increases limits. Pro at $20/month offers higher presentation counts and premium features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'slidesai';

-- Decktopus
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Decktopus?</h2><p>Decktopus is an AI presentation maker that builds ready-to-present decks from a topic or outline. Beyond generating slides, it provides AI content suggestions as you edit and includes built-in forms and call-to-action buttons that turn presentations into interactive lead capture tools. Sales teams and educators find this combination of AI generation and interactivity particularly useful.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI deck generation from topics or outlines. Contextual content suggestions throughout the editing process. Embedded forms and call-to-action buttons for lead generation. Custom domain publishing for branded presentation sharing. Viewer analytics track engagement and completion rates.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan offers limited features. The AI plan at $14.99/month includes full generation capabilities. Business at $29.99/month adds collaboration and branding features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'decktopus';

-- Presentations.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Presentations.ai?</h2><p>Presentations.ai is an AI-first presentation platform that focuses on delivering design quality that rivals agency work. Type a prompt or upload a document, and it produces polished, visually diverse slide decks in seconds. The output quality is noticeably more varied and creative than most competitors, making it a good fit for teams that need to impress clients or stakeholders with visual impact.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>High-quality visual design output that competes with professional agencies. Very fast generation from prompts or documents. An editable slide layout system for fine-tuning. PowerPoint and PDF export for universal sharing. A growing library of professional templates.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan includes limited monthly AI credits. Pro at $19/month offers unlimited generation and premium features. Team plans are available for collaborative use.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'presentations-ai';

-- Kroma AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Kroma AI?</h2><p>Kroma AI is a presentation platform built for teams that need to maintain strict brand consistency across every deck they produce. It uses AI to generate slides while enforcing brand guidelines — ensuring fonts, colors, logos, and layout patterns stay on-brand regardless of who creates the presentation. Marketing and design teams managing brand standards across large organizations find this particularly valuable.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI slide generation with automatic brand guideline enforcement. Style guide integration keeps fonts, colors, and layouts consistent. Smart layout adaptation adjusts designs to content changes. A professional template library covers common business needs. Team collaboration features support multi-person editing.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Starter plans begin at $25/month. Team and Business tiers add brand management capabilities and multiple user access.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'kroma-ai';

-- Storydoc
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Storydoc?</h2><p>Storydoc reimagines presentations as interactive, web-native experiences rather than static slide decks. Instead of clicking through slides, recipients scroll through a dynamic web page with embedded videos, live data, and personalized sections. Detailed engagement analytics show exactly which sections each recipient spent time on, making it a powerful tool for B2B sales teams looking to understand prospect interest.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Interactive, scrollable web-based presentation format. Per-recipient personalization customizes content for each viewer. Slide-by-slide engagement heatmaps reveal what interests each prospect. CRM integrations with HubSpot and Salesforce sync engagement data. AI content assistance helps write compelling copy.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Starter plan at $40/month covers basic needs. Team plans support collaborative sales deck creation. Enterprise plans include custom integrations and SSO.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'storydoc';

-- Pitch
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Pitch?</h2><p>Pitch is a modern collaborative presentation platform that combines beautiful design with real-time team editing, similar to how Figma transformed design collaboration. AI content generation helps build slides faster, while the collaboration features — live cursors, threaded comments, version history — make it ideal for teams that build decks together rather than in isolation. Startups and agencies particularly gravitate toward it.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Real-time multi-user collaboration with live cursors and comments. AI-powered slide generation and content suggestions. Over 100 professionally designed templates. Presentation analytics track viewer engagement. Slack integration makes sharing seamless across teams.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes unlimited decks with limited workspaces. Pro at $22/month per user adds custom branding, analytics, and priority features. Business and Enterprise plans offer advanced admin controls.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'pitch-com';

-- Prezi AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Prezi AI?</h2><p>Prezi AI takes the signature Prezi zooming canvas and enhances it with AI-powered content and design generation. Instead of clicking through flat slides, Prezi presentations fly across a visual map, zooming into details and pulling back to show the big picture. The effect is cinematic and memorable, though it can also overwhelm audiences if overused. AI features now help generate that non-linear content structure automatically.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The iconic zoomable canvas creates dynamic, non-linear presentations. AI generates content and layouts tailored to the zooming format. Prezi Video overlays your presentation on video calls for engaging virtual meetings. Audience analytics track how people interact with shared presentations. A large template library covers diverse use cases.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan includes Prezi branding. Standard at $19/month removes branding. Plus and Premium plans add privacy controls, advanced analytics, and higher storage limits.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'prezi-ai';

-- ===== AI Automation & Sales (18 tools) =====

-- n8n
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is n8n?</h2><p>n8n is a fair-code licensed workflow automation platform that offers something unique: you can self-host it on your own servers for free. This makes it the tool of choice for technical teams that need full control over their data and infrastructure. With over 400 integrations, a visual node-based editor, and the ability to write custom JavaScript or Python code within any workflow, n8n is automation for people who also know how to code.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Free self-hosted option with complete data privacy. Over 400 pre-built integrations with popular services. Custom JavaScript and Python code nodes for advanced logic. AI-native nodes integrate LLMs like GPT-4 and Claude directly into automations. The visual editor makes complex workflows understandable at a glance.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The self-hosted Community Edition is completely free. Cloud Starter begins at $20/month. Team and Enterprise tiers offer advanced permissions, SSO, and dedicated support.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'n8n';

-- Activepieces
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Activepieces?</h2><p>Activepieces is an open-source, no-code automation platform that positions itself as the free alternative to Zapier and Make. Like n8n, it supports self-hosting, but its interface is designed for non-technical users who want drag-and-drop simplicity. The TypeScript SDK allows developers to create custom integrations — or "pieces" — extending the platform beyond its 200+ built-in connectors.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Completely free self-hosted version with no feature restrictions. Over 200 built-in integrations for common business tools. A clean, intuitive visual builder accessible to non-technical users. TypeScript SDK for building custom integrations. AI pieces connect to ChatGPT, Claude, and other language models.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Self-hosted is free and open source. The cloud free plan includes 1,000 tasks per month. Paid plans offer higher task limits and team collaboration features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'activepieces';

-- Pipedream
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Pipedream?</h2><p>Pipedream is a developer-first workflow automation platform that uniquely blends no-code triggers with real code steps. Unlike pure no-code tools, Pipedream lets you drop in full Node.js, Python, Go, or Bash code at any point in your workflow. Every workflow runs serverlessly on Pipedream''s infrastructure, so you avoid managing servers while still having the full power of a programming language at your fingertips.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Mix no-code actions with full code steps in the same workflow. Support for Node.js, Python, Go, and Bash. Over 1,000 app integrations with pre-built triggers and actions. Serverless execution means no infrastructure management. Event sources listen to webhooks, poll APIs, and subscribe to event streams.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan provides 10,000 invocations per month. Paid plans start at $29/month for higher limits and advanced features like longer execution times.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'pipedream';

-- Workato
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Workato?</h2><p>Workato is an enterprise-grade intelligent automation platform that serves Fortune 500 companies. It combines integration (iPaaS), RPA, and AI into a single platform, with over 1,000 pre-built connectors that link business applications together. Workato''s AI suggests automation recipes and its Workbot delivers automation results directly inside Slack and Microsoft Teams, making it popular with enterprise IT and operations teams.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Over 1,000 pre-built connectors for enterprise applications. AI-powered recipe suggestions speed up automation creation. Workbot integrates automation into Slack and Microsoft Teams. RPA capabilities handle legacy system interactions. Enterprise-grade security and compliance certifications.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Enterprise pricing typically starts around $15,000/year with custom quotes based on usage. A free trial is available. Pricing depends on workspace usage, recipe count, and task volume.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'workato';

-- Tray.io
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Tray.io?</h2><p>Tray.io (now Tray AI) is an enterprise automation platform that specializes in complex, multi-step integrations between SaaS applications. Its low-code workflow builder supports conditional logic, loops, and data transformations that go well beyond simple trigger-action patterns. Revenue operations and marketing operations teams use it to connect CRM, marketing automation, and data warehouse tools.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Advanced workflow builder with conditional logic, loops, and data transformation. Universal Connector integrates with any REST API. Merlin AI provides intelligent automation suggestions and troubleshooting. Enterprise-grade security and compliance. Purpose-built for complex RevOps and MarketingOps use cases.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Enterprise pricing typically starts around $12,000/year with custom quotes. A free trial is available upon request. Pricing depends on workflow count, executions, and team size.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'tray-io';

-- Bardeen AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Bardeen?</h2><p>Bardeen is an AI-powered browser automation tool that lets you automate repetitive web tasks using natural language. Install the Chrome extension, describe what you want to automate in plain English, and the Magic Box AI builds the workflow for you. Sales reps use it to scrape LinkedIn profiles into their CRM, recruiters automate candidate sourcing, and marketers pull data from competing websites — all without writing a single line of code.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Natural language commands create automations through the Magic Box AI. No-code browser automation handles web-based tasks. Hundreds of pre-built playbooks cover common sales, recruiting, and marketing workflows. Works directly within your browser on any website. CRM integration syncs scraped data with your existing tools.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan covers basic automations. Pro starts at $10/month (billed annually) with premium integrations and higher usage limits. Enterprise plans offer team management features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'bardeen-ai';

-- Browse AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Browse AI?</h2><p>Browse AI is a no-code web scraping platform that uses AI to train robots for data extraction. Instead of writing code, you click on the data you want on any website, and Browse AI creates a scraping robot that can run on a schedule. It handles JavaScript-rendered pages, logged-in sessions, and pagination — the kinds of technical challenges that typically require developer expertise to solve.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Point-and-click interface for creating web scrapers without code. Handles JavaScript-heavy websites and dynamic content. Change monitoring sends alerts when tracked data changes. Scheduled robot runs keep your data fresh. Export to Google Sheets, Airtable, or via API.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan includes 50 credits per month. Paid plans start at $19/month with more credits and higher-frequency scheduling. Credits are consumed per robot run.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'browse-ai';

-- Apify
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Apify?</h2><p>Apify is a full-featured web scraping and automation platform with a marketplace of over 1,500 pre-built scrapers called Actors. Need to scrape Google search results, Amazon product listings, or Instagram profiles? There is probably an Actor for that already. For custom needs, developers can build their own Actors using the Node.js or Python SDK, while the platform handles the infrastructure — proxy rotation, CAPTCHA solving, and anti-bot bypassing.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>A marketplace of 1,500+ pre-built scrapers for popular websites. Managed proxy rotation and anti-bot bypass infrastructure. SDKs for Node.js and Python enable custom scraper development. Cloud storage for scraped datasets with API export. The platform handles scheduling, retries, and error handling automatically.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes $5 of platform credits per month. Paid plans start at $49/month for more compute, storage, and proxy resources. Usage-based pricing applies beyond plan limits.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'apify';

-- PhantomBuster
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is PhantomBuster?</h2><p>PhantomBuster is a cloud-based automation tool built for growth hackers and sales teams who need to automate lead generation across social platforms. Its library of over 100 pre-built Phantoms covers LinkedIn profile scraping, automated connection requests, Twitter engagement, Instagram data extraction, and more. Everything runs in the cloud, so your automations keep working even when your computer is off.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>100+ pre-built automation templates for LinkedIn, Twitter, Instagram, and more. Flows chain multiple Phantoms into end-to-end lead generation pipelines. Cloud-based execution means automations run 24/7. No coding required for most use cases. Email finding and data enrichment capabilities.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan includes 2 hours of execution per month. Paid plans start at $56/month (billed annually) with more execution time and parallel Phantom slots.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'phantombuster';

-- Clay
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Clay?</h2><p>Clay has become the most powerful tool in the modern outbound sales stack. It aggregates data from 75+ enrichment sources — LinkedIn, Apollo, Clearbit, and many more — to build comprehensive lead profiles. Then its AI writes hyper-personalized email copy for each prospect at scale. The "waterfall enrichment" approach tries multiple data providers sequentially to maximize data coverage, solving the poor-data problem that has always plagued outbound sales.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>75+ data enrichment sources for building detailed lead profiles. Waterfall enrichment maximizes data coverage by trying multiple providers. AI-powered personalized email copy generation at scale. Claygent, an AI research agent, performs custom prospect research automatically. CRM sync keeps enriched data updated in your existing tools.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan includes 100 credits. Paid plans start at $149/month with more credits and features. Credits are consumed per enrichment lookup. Enterprise plans serve high-volume teams.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'clay-hq';

-- Lemlist
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Lemlist?</h2><p>Lemlist is a cold email and multichannel outreach platform known for its innovative personalization features. Beyond standard mail merge, Lemlist lets you dynamically personalize images and videos in your emails — think a screenshot showing the prospect''s website or a video with their name on a whiteboard. Combined with lemwarm (their email warm-up tool) and LinkedIn automation, it is a complete outreach toolkit for sales teams.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Dynamic image and video personalization for each recipient. Built-in email warm-up through lemwarm improves deliverability. Multichannel sequences combine email, LinkedIn, and calls in one workflow. AI writing assistance generates personalized email copy. Strong deliverability features help emails reach the inbox.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Plans start at $39/month per seat for email outreach. Multichannel plans at $59/month add LinkedIn automation. Annual billing offers significant discounts.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'lemlist';

-- Instantly AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Instantly?</h2><p>Instantly.ai is a cold email platform designed for scale, and its defining feature is unlimited email sending accounts on all paid plans. Agencies managing dozens of client campaigns and high-volume outbound teams no longer need to calculate per-account costs. Every account includes built-in email warm-up, and the AI personalizes emails across large lead lists to maintain both deliverability and response rates.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Unlimited email sending accounts on every paid plan. Built-in warm-up for all connected email accounts. AI writing assistant personalizes emails at scale. Comprehensive deliverability analytics track campaign health. A built-in lead database allows prospecting within the platform.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Growth plan at $37/month includes 1,000 active leads and 5,000 emails monthly. Hypergrowth at $97/month increases limits significantly. A 14-day free trial is available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'instantly-ai';

-- Apollo.io
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Apollo.io?</h2><p>Apollo.io is one of the most popular all-in-one sales intelligence platforms, combining a massive database of 270 million contacts and 60 million companies with built-in outreach tools. Sales teams find prospects, enrich their CRM data, launch email sequences, and track engagement without leaving the platform. The generous free tier makes it accessible to startups, while enterprise features scale to large sales organizations.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>A database of 270M+ contacts and 60M+ companies with detailed filtering. Built-in email sequencing and outreach automation. A LinkedIn Chrome extension enriches profiles with contact data. AI email writing and lead scoring prioritize the best opportunities. Intent data signals identify companies actively researching solutions.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan includes 10 email credits per month. Basic at $49/user/month provides 900 credits. Professional and Organization plans increase limits and add advanced features.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'apollo-io';

-- Smartlead AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Smartlead?</h2><p>Smartlead.ai is a cold email platform built with agencies in mind. Like Instantly, it offers unlimited mailboxes on all plans, but adds white-label capabilities that let agencies brand the platform for their clients. Smart mailbox rotation distributes sending across accounts to maximize deliverability, and the master inbox consolidates replies from all campaigns into one view.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Unlimited mailboxes on all paid plans. White-label option lets agencies brand the platform. Smart rotation distributes emails across mailboxes for deliverability. AI-powered warm-up maintains sender reputation on all accounts. A master inbox consolidates replies from every campaign.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Basic plan starts at $39/month with 2,000 active leads. Pro at $94/month adds higher limits and advanced features. A 14-day free trial is available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'smartlead-ai';

-- Gong.io
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Gong?</h2><p>Gong is the market leader in revenue intelligence, capturing and analyzing every customer interaction — calls, emails, meetings — to surface the patterns that separate winning deals from lost ones. Sales leaders use Gong to coach reps with timestamped call feedback, forecast revenue with AI-powered accuracy, and understand exactly which behaviors correlate with closing deals. It has become an essential tool for data-driven sales organizations.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI-powered call analysis identifies topics, competitor mentions, and deal risks automatically. Deal intelligence tracks engagement and predicts likelihood to close. Coaching tools let managers leave timestamped comments on call recordings. Accurate revenue forecasting aids pipeline management. Deep CRM integration syncs insights with your existing tools.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Enterprise pricing typically ranges from $1,200 to $1,600 per user annually plus a platform fee. Minimum contracts are usually required. Contact sales for a custom quote.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'gong-io';

-- Chorus.ai
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Chorus.ai?</h2><p>Chorus.ai, acquired by ZoomInfo in 2021, is a conversation intelligence platform that analyzes sales calls, video meetings, and email threads. As part of the ZoomInfo ecosystem, it combines conversation analysis with contact intelligence data for a fuller picture of each deal. Teams already using ZoomInfo for prospecting data get the most value from Chorus, since both platforms share a unified view of buyer engagement.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>AI transcription and analysis of sales calls and meetings. Key moment detection identifies next steps, competitor mentions, and pricing discussions. Coaching scorecards evaluate rep performance against defined criteria. Deep ZoomInfo integration enriches call analysis with prospect data. Deal intelligence tracks multi-threaded engagement across buying committees.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Enterprise pricing is typically bundled with ZoomInfo subscriptions. Contact ZoomInfo for custom pricing. A demo is available upon request.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'chorus-ai';

-- Exceed AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Exceed.ai?</h2><p>Exceed.ai is an AI-powered virtual sales assistant that automates the top of the sales funnel. It engages leads via email and chat, asking qualifying questions in natural two-way conversations and scheduling meetings with human sales reps when a lead is ready. For high-volume teams drowning in unqualified leads, Exceed acts as an always-on SDR that handles initial qualification without human intervention.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Automated two-way email conversations that feel natural. Lead qualification based on customizable criteria. Automatic meeting scheduling with human reps when leads are ready. Objection handling and FAQ responses. CRM integration keeps all lead data synchronized. Now part of the Genesys platform.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Enterprise pricing starts around $2,000/month depending on volume and features. Contact sales for a custom quote and demo.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'exceed-ai';

-- Salesloft
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Salesloft?</h2><p>Salesloft is a leading AI-powered sales engagement platform managing the full revenue lifecycle — from prospecting cadences through deal management to forecasting. After acquiring Drift, the conversational AI company, Salesloft now covers buyer engagement at every stage. Enterprise sales teams use it to orchestrate multi-channel outreach, analyze conversations for coaching insights, and predict quarterly revenue with AI-powered accuracy.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Sales cadence automation across email, phone, and LinkedIn. Conversation intelligence analyzes calls and meetings for coaching insights. AI-powered forecasting predicts quarterly revenue performance. Deal management tracks opportunities through the pipeline. Drift integration adds conversational buyer engagement.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Enterprise pricing typically starts around $125/user/month with minimum seat requirements. Annual contracts are standard. Contact sales for a custom quote.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'salesloft';

-- ===== AI SEO & Marketing (12 tools) =====

-- Surfer SEO
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Surfer SEO?</h2><p>Surfer SEO takes the guesswork out of on-page optimization. It analyzes the top-ranking pages for your target keyword across 500+ factors and provides a precise content brief that tells you exactly what to include. The Content Editor scores your article in real time as you write, and the Surfer AI feature can generate entire SEO-optimized articles automatically. For content teams that publish at volume, Surfer provides the data-driven framework that turns good writing into content that ranks.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Real-time content scoring against the top-ranking pages for any keyword. Topical Map identifies content gaps across your entire site. Surfer AI generates full SEO-optimized articles from a keyword. Integration with Google Docs and WordPress for seamless workflow. SERP analysis and keyword research tools round out the suite.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The Essential plan starts at $89/month (billed annually) with 30 articles. Scale at $129/month increases limits and adds team features. A 7-day free trial is available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'surfer-seo';

-- Clearscope
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Clearscope?</h2><p>Clearscope is a premium content optimization platform used by enterprise content teams and top SEO agencies. It analyzes the highest-ranking content for a keyword and provides recommendations weighted by relevance — not just a keyword list, but a nuanced view of which concepts matter most. The letter grade system (A+ to F) gives writers a clear quality target, while Google Docs and WordPress integrations make optimizing content seamless.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Term recommendations weighted by semantic relevance, not just frequency. Letter grade scoring gives clear quality targets. Deep Google Docs and WordPress integration. Clean, distraction-free interface focused on content quality. Trusted by prominent content teams and SEO agencies worldwide.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Essentials starts at $199/month with 50 content reports. Business plans begin at $599/month for higher limits. Enterprise plans are custom. A free demo is available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'clearscope';

-- MarketMuse
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is MarketMuse?</h2><p>MarketMuse is a content intelligence platform for strategists and SEO managers making high-level decisions about content investment. Rather than optimizing individual pages, it analyzes your entire website against competitors to identify where you have topical authority and where gaps exist. This strategic perspective helps content teams decide not just how to write, but what to write and in what order for maximum ranking impact.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Topic Model analyzes your site''s topical coverage relative to competitors. Content Inventory audits existing pages and prioritizes optimization opportunities. Automated content briefs include recommended topics, questions, and word counts. Strategic content planning based on competitive authority gaps. Free plan available for initial exploration.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>The free plan provides 10 queries per month. Standard at $149/month unlocks unlimited queries. Team and Premium plans offer personalized AI models trained on your specific content.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'marketmuse';

-- Frase SEO
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Frase?</h2><p>Frase combines SERP research, content briefing, and AI writing into a single workflow at a price point well below Surfer SEO and Clearscope. It analyzes the top 20 search results for any keyword and auto-generates a content brief covering headings, topics, and featured snippet opportunities. The built-in AI writer can then draft sections of your article based on the brief. For freelancers and small agencies, Frase offers serious SEO tooling without the premium price tag.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Auto-generated content briefs from top 20 SERP analysis. Content scoring tracks how well your article covers important topics. AI writer generates outlines, introductions, and full sections. Question research pulls from People Also Ask boxes. Collaborative document editing for team workflows.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Solo at $45/month includes 4 articles. Basic at $115/month removes article limits. A Pro AI add-on for unlimited writing is $35/month additional.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'frase-seo';

-- Semrush AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Semrush?</h2><p>Semrush is the most comprehensive digital marketing platform in the industry, used by millions of marketing professionals worldwide. Its toolkit spans keyword research, competitor analysis, backlink auditing, site audits, content marketing, PPC, and social media. AI features have been layered throughout — ContentShake AI drafts SEO content, Copilot proactively surfaces insights from your data, and AI keyword clustering groups related terms automatically.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>A keyword database of 25+ billion keywords across global markets. Copilot AI proactively analyzes your project data and surfaces recommendations. ContentShake AI drafts SEO-optimized articles from keyword research. Backlink Audit identifies and helps disavow toxic links. Site Audit crawls your website and prioritizes technical SEO fixes.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A limited free plan is available. Pro at $139.95/month suits individuals. Guru at $249.95/month adds content marketing tools. Business at $499.95/month includes API access and white-label reports.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'semrush-ai';

-- Ahrefs AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Ahrefs?</h2><p>Ahrefs is one of the most trusted SEO toolsets among professional SEOs, celebrated for its massive and frequently updated backlink index. Content Explorer, which indexes over 14 billion web pages, is unmatched for link-building research and content gap analysis. Recent AI additions include AI-powered keyword clustering and a content grader that evaluates your pages against top-ranking competitors — adding intelligence to an already indispensable dataset.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>The industry''s most comprehensive backlink index. Keywords Explorer offers AI-powered clustering to reveal topical coverage gaps. Content Explorer indexes 14+ billion pages for research and prospecting. AI Content Grader evaluates pages against ranking competitors. Site Audit identifies technical SEO issues with prioritized fix recommendations.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Lite at $129/month covers core tools with 5 projects. Standard at $249/month adds more credits and historical data. Advanced and Enterprise plans expand access further.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'ahrefs-ai';

-- NeuronWriter
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is NeuronWriter?</h2><p>NeuronWriter approaches content optimization differently from most tools. Instead of counting keyword frequency, it uses NLP and semantic analysis to identify the concepts and entities that correlate with top rankings. The result is recommendations that feel more natural and less keyword-stuffed. Integration with Google Search Console grounds its suggestions in your site''s actual performance data, and the built-in AI writer handles content drafting.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>NLP-based semantic analysis goes beyond simple keyword counting. Term recommendations grouped by semantic relevance. Google Search Console integration shows real performance alongside optimization suggestions. AI writing assistant generates optimized content from keyword research. Content planner serves as an editorial calendar for SEO-driven teams.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Plans start at $23/month for the Bronze tier with 25 analyses. Lifetime deal options occasionally appear on deal platforms. Higher tiers include more analyses and team seats.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'neuronwriter';

-- Page Optimizer Pro
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Page Optimizer Pro?</h2><p>Page Optimizer Pro (POP) was built by Kyle Roof, who conducted systematic, controlled testing of hundreds of Google ranking factors. The result is a tool that provides unusually precise, tag-level recommendations — telling you exactly how many times to place a keyword in your title tag, H1, H2 headers, and body text based on what actually correlates with rankings. Advanced SEOs who want granular, data-backed optimization guidance consider POP essential.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Tag-level recommendations based on controlled ranking factor tests. Factor-by-factor analysis shows ideal usage for each HTML element. Schema markup recommendations add structured data to pages. Content grading provides an overall optimization score. An AI writer generates content aligned with POP''s analysis.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Basic at $34/month includes 20 page reports. Premium at $84/month increases reports and adds bulk features. A free trial is available.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'page-optimizer-pro';

-- Alli AI
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Alli AI?</h2><p>Alli AI addresses the implementation gap that plagues SEO — the distance between knowing what needs to change and actually making those changes across hundreds or thousands of pages. Most tools tell you what to fix; Alli AI can deploy fixes automatically by directly editing your website''s code. For agencies managing large client sites, this ability to implement title tags, meta descriptions, schema markup, and internal links at scale is a massive time saver.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Bulk optimization identifies opportunities across entire websites simultaneously. One-click deployment implements approved SEO changes without manual editing. Schema markup automation adds structured data at scale. Internal link optimization improves site-wide link structure. White-label capabilities suit agency use cases.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>Consultant at $299/month covers 10 websites. Agency at $599/month supports 25 websites. Enterprise plans are custom-priced.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'alli-ai';

-- Diib
UPDATE ai_tools
SET content_html = '<h2>What Is Diib?</h2><p>Diib is designed for small business owners and non-technical marketers who want SEO insights without the complexity of professional tools. Connect your Google Analytics and Search Console accounts, and Diib''s AI delivers a daily health score, growth alerts, and competitive benchmarking in plain, actionable language. It will not replace Ahrefs or Semrush for serious SEOs, but for someone running a local business who just wants to know what to improve next, Diib is refreshingly simple.</p><h2>Key Features</h2><p>Daily website health score distills complex metrics into a single number. Automated growth opportunity alerts surface what to work on next. Competitive benchmarking compares your performance against similar sites. Direct Google Analytics and Search Console integration uses your real data. Answer engine explains SEO concepts in simple language.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>A free plan provides basic insights. Pro plans start at $29/month for deeper analysis and more detailed recommendations.</p>'
WHERE slug = 'diib';
